attributes.title: Onnit Assessment
attributes.description: After working out 6 times a week for 6 weeks Ellie checks in with the team at Onnit to find out her final assessment numbers

attributes.title: Chad Rides a Unicorn at Full Sail
attributes.description: Join Alfredo, Chad & Brian as they travel to Brian's alma mater, Full Sail University, for Hall of Fame Week. There’s gonna be RC Mario Kart, there’s gonna be Unicorns, there’s gonna be a Super 80s Fighter Project. Thanks to Full Sail University for partnering with us to make this video. If you'd like to find out more about Full Sail, click here: http://bit.ly/2D192o0.

attributes.title: The NEW RoosterTeeth.com Video Site is Coming March 30!
attributes.description: It’s been a long time coming, but we’ve heard your (many) thoughts, and made some changes…The NEW Roosterteeth.com video platform is almost here! Check out the beta at svod.roosterteeth.com to see what’s in progress, give us your feedback, and stay tuned for more to come!

attributes.title: Goodbye old RoosterTeeth.com!
attributes.description: With the launch of the new RoosterTeeth.com video site and mobile apps less than a week away, we decided we would take some work off the tech team’s plate, and lend a hand by destroying the old site!

attributes.title: RoosterTeeth.com Eaten by a Bear?!
attributes.description: It's time to say hello, because the new RoosterTeeth.com video site and mobile apps are finally available! We hope you enjoy your experience - no spirit guide required!

attributes.title: Founders Throwback: Probing the Annals
attributes.description: Gus and Burnie watch OG videos from back in the day for a little probe down memory lane. The Lab wants to explore RT's humble beginnings so we can push into the future.

attributes.title: RWBY Meets Todd McFarlane
attributes.description:
Barbara and Lindsay take a tour of the McFarlane studio, getting a first look at the new limited edition RWBY Alpha Beowolf Battle Statue and meeting the creators behind the magic. 

Add this epic piece to your collection today, complete with a certificate of authenticity hand signed by Todd McFarlane and Kerry Shawcross. For more information, clips, and a full gallery of the statue, check out https://www.rwbystatue.com/.

attributes.title: The Art Director
attributes.description: Filmmaker and auteur Max Kruemcke examines the life and legacy of the renowned Art Director, Max Kruemcke, a man of intense personal drive and "immaculate execution" who has a transformative effect on those around him. Critics are calling this film "technically a movie" and it has been nominated by renowned fulm festivals: The Cannot Film Festival, NSFW and Sundaes.
